quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  43,74,"Pellet, bon…ďe …ďen, ko ka lepte Jahannama …ďe luttoyta,"
  43,75,"…ďe koynantaake, tee hara ko …ďe ta∆īii…ďe toon."
  43,76,"Min too√Īaani …ďe few, si ko woni, ko kam…ďe woni too√Īu…ďe …ďeen."
  43,77,"∆Āe nodda: "Ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen !" O wi'i: "Pellet, ko on luttoo…ďe [toon] !""
  43,78,""GooŇč…óii Min ngaddanii on goonga kan ; kono …óuu…óu…ďe e mon, ko a√Ī…ďe goonga"."
  43,79,"Kaa …ďe e…ď…ďu fehre ? Doo ko Min fewjoo…ďe !"
  43,80,"Maa hara …ďe cikku Min nanataa gunndooji ma…ď…ďe e sirru ma…ď…ďe? Oo‚Äôowoye! Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďeen hino maandina takko ma…ď…ďe."
  43,81,"Maaku: "Si Hinaranko on no njogitii …ďi…ó…óo, ko miin adotonoo rewude oon"."
  43,82,"Senaare woodanii Jey…óo kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, Jey…óo Arsi kin; laa…ďu…óo e kon ko …ďe cifrotta mo."
  43,83,"Accu…ďe …ďe jumpa, …ďe pija haa …ďe hawroya e √Īalaande ma…ď…ďe nde…ďe fodaa."
  43,84,"Ko KaŇčko woni On dewetee…óo ka kammu e dewetee…óo ka leydi, ko KaŇčko kadi woni √Ďee√Īo, ganndu…óo On."
  43,85,"Barke heewanii on mo woodani …óum, laamu kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka makko anndal fii Darngal woni. Ko ka makko kadi nduttete…óon."
  43,86,"∆äi …ďe ndewata …óin ga makko jeyah tefoore, si wonaa seedii…ďe goonga …ďeen, hara he…ďe nganndi."
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ďe, ko hommbo woni ko tagi …ďe? ∆Āe mbi'ay: "Ko Allah". Ko holno non …ďe njiiliraa?"
  43,88,"[Himo anndi kadi] fii ko (Nulaa…óo) oon maakunoo kon: "Ko an yo Joomi, pellet, …ďee ko yim…ďe …ďe ngooŇč…óintaa"."
  43,89,"Yaafo …ďe, maakaa: "Kisal !" Aray ndebe ngannda."